CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777428225
OL,3,CMPs vote against investigation into
OL,4,Cwhether Starmer misled parliament
OL,6,FDespite the victory, a handful of
OL,7,Fbackbenchers broke ranks on Tuesday to
OL,8,Fcriticise the government for whipping
OL,9,Fits MPs to oppose the motion, and
OL,10,Fsuggested the prime minister should
OL,11,Frefer himself to the Privileges
OL,12,FCommittee to "clear his name".
OL,14,FFifteen Labour MPs rebelled against
OL,15,Fthe whip and backed Kemi Badenoch's
OL,16,Fmotion, along with Hull MP Karl
OL,17,FTurner, who recently lost the Labour
OL,18,Fwhip over his opposition to plans to
OL,19,Flimit jury trials.
OL,26,@tD@NOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
