OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777428225
OL,3,CMPs vote against investigation into
OL,4,Cwhether Starmer misled parliament
OL,6,FSir Keir himself attended the Commons
OL,7,Fon Tuesday evening to vote against the
OL,8,Fmotion.
OL,10,FAfter the vote, a Downing Street
OL,11,Fspokesman said the government was
OL,12,F"delivering for Britain" while the
OL,13,FConservatives had "resorted to this
OL,14,Fdesperate political stunt" ahead of
OL,15,Flocal elections "because they have no
OL,16,Fanswers on the cost of living or the
OL,17,FNHS".
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@XO]uD@SOUvD@ZO]wD@QOUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
