OL,3,CMPs vote against investigation into
OL,4,Cwhether Starmer misled parliament
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,7,Faccused the prime minister of
OL,8,Fcowardice saying: "Starmer has ducked
OL,9,Fthe scrutiny he should have faced by
OL,10,Fforcing Labour MPs to defend him. What
OL,11,Fa cowardly way to govern.
OL,13,F"If he truly felt his conduct over the
OL,14,FMandelson scandal was up to scratch he
OL,15,Fshould have undergone investigation by
OL,16,Fthe Privileges Committee."
OL,26,@pD@SOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
