OL,3,CMPs vote against investigation into
OL,4,Cwhether Starmer misled parliament
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FEarlier on Tuesday, two ex-officials
OL,12,Fgave evidence on Mandelson's
OL,13,Fappointment and security vetting to
OL,14,FMPs on the Foreign Affairs Select
OL,15,FCommittee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
