PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777428225
OL,3,CMPs vote against investigation into
OL,4,Cwhether Starmer misled parliament
OL,6,FThe results of the vote on Tuesday
OL,7,Fcame as parliament's Intelligence and
OL,8,FSecurity Committee (ISC) said it had
OL,9,Ffinished reviewing the government's
OL,10,Fproposed redactions to documents
OL,11,Frelating to Lord Mandelson's
OL,12,Fappointment ahead of publication.
OL,14,FMPs ordered the government to publish
OL,15,Fa huge tranche of documents connected
OL,16,Fto the appointment in February, but so
OL,17,Ffar only a handful have been released.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777428225
OL,3,CMPs vote against investigation into
OL,4,Cwhether Starmer misled parliament
OL,6,FThe government has asked to redact
OL,7,Fsome of the documents requested for
OL,8,Fnational security reasons, or because
OL,9,Fthey relate to a police investigation
OL,10,Finto allegations against Lord
OL,11,FMandelson of misconduct in public
OL,12,Foffice, which the peer denies.
OL,14,FIn a statement on Tuesday, ISC
OL,15,Fchairman Lord Beamish said his
OL,16,Fcommittee had reached decisions on all
OL,17,Fthe proposed redactions, including
OL,18,Fsome requested within the previous 24
OL,19,Fhours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
