FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777428225
OL,3,CMPs vote against investigation into
OL,4,Cwhether Starmer misled parliament
OL,6,FThe government could still challenge
OL,7,Fthose decisions at a private committee
OL,8,Fhearing, which would take place after
OL,9,Fthe state opening of Parliament next
OL,10,Fmonth.
OL,12,FParliament will break later this week
OL,13,Fahead of May's local elections.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
